@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.16)) - ((v2 + 0.67 - v2 + 0.41) + wp.cos(v1 + 0.04)))
    tmp = (tmp / (0.84 * 0.07))
    data[tid] = v0
